data.description: Nice home that needs some minor cleaning. Inside the house, the kitchens and bathrooms have been updated and the house has a great floor plan, which opens to a wooded, fenced backyard. The house has an attractive curb appeal and is located on a quiet dead end street with a wooded front yard. Owner states house has a newer roof and then Hurricane Ian dropped a branch on the roof and caused a roof leak over the garage (currently tarped). The house should qualify for FHA with needed roof repair. Quick possession possible. SELLER IS CURRENTLY OFFERING $10,000 "FLEX CASH" to buy buyer's interest rate down, pay buyer's closing costs, or credit for any repairs.
